Product Version     25.10    Cadence Design Systems, Inc.
report_pg_keepout(25.10)                              report_pg_keepout(25.10)

Name
       report_pg_keepout

Syntax
        report_pg_keepout

       [-help]

       [-file <file_name>]

       {-cell <lib_cell_name> | -inst <instance_name>}

       Reports all PG keepout boxes in the design if no option is specified.

Parameters
       -cell lib_cell_name
              Reports PG keepout boxes applied to the specified lib cell only.

       -file <file_name>
              Specifies the file name where all the details are dumped.

              -help"  Outputs  a  brief description that includes type and de-
              fault information for each report_pg_keepout parameter.

              For a detailed description of the command and all of its parame-
              ters, use the man command: man report_pg_keepout

       -inst instance_name
              Reports PG keepout boxes applied to the specified instance only.

Related Information
              * specify_pg_keepout

              * delete_pg_keepout

